{"tid":2010143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪私隱專員強烈譴責有人針對立法會保安人員起底 下令移除有關帖文","createTime":"2020-05-10T08:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T09:07:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"96da1a134cfff1dee356c5a7513dab9428142b54","tid":2010143,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"私隱專員強烈譴責有人針對立法會保安人員「起底」<br />\n10.05.2020 16:30<br />\n<br />\n私隱專員黃繼兒表示，注意到有立法會保安人員，在日前的內務委員會會議執勤後，被人在社交平台「起底」，除了披露包括家人的個人資料，更有人表示或鼓吹對保安人員的妻兒不利。黃繼兒強烈讉責「令人不齒的個人資料武器化」行為，令受害人尤其在執行職務時，受到不合理和不必要的壓力和傷害。個人資料私隱專員公署會主動展開調查，要求有關人士立即停止「起底」，並會去信涉事的社交網絡平台，立即移除有關帖文。公署亦會將涉嫌違反法庭禁制令的個案，轉介律政司跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286471&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286471%26csid%3D261_341&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=6fdde826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286471&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2fa1406695a54611acd0b49e9416f6791e47ec28","tid":2010143,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"啋你都傻"},{"pid":"61dd226542515aaa49b4fa162bb65dca145a57de","tid":2010143,"uid":3776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"起埋私穩專員"},{"pid":"3fa877f22df34fd88c2fbbc675e902cf1b89e9e7","tid":2010143,"uid":266342,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"有本事去美國撳個掣delete佢啊笨<br />\n支那畜真係支那畜，智障到不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8b83862c3a1407fbd678a77a62902d2b5470ab","tid":2010143,"uid":91771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"又係時候掉上blockchain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7370fcba84dee0f64a674166f90dc81e7b57e4b5","tid":2010143,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"支那狗唔係驚呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地最暴力架嘛"},{"pid":"355491dddddd4949e0a99acbff34195fd69d78d1","tid":2010143,"uid":28432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"撐牆消防妻　全家遭警起底<br />\n2019-07-14<br />\n頭條<br />\n <br />\n消防妻「阿欣」對一家三口被起底感到懼怕，減少出街避風頭。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n【白色恐怖】<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵油塘站外連日有不同意見的市民就《逃犯條例》表態引發衝突，當中衝突點「連儂牆」對開，前晚有休班警員被指在場拍攝市民，遭多人包圍起哄，警方上前護送該名警員離開，混亂間一名女子跌倒在地上。該名反對《逃犯條例》的女子昨指事後她全家遭「起底」，並在警察群組公開，包括她和家人相片及工作地址等，昨晨女事主在上班時更遭人用手機拍攝，她已聯絡立法會議員日內陪同報案，冀遏止個人私隱被公開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉晒班差佬未？要知個警察群組班人身分唔難喎 仲唔拉人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdd527b0b0f6e6446e1e7d2a3371dd5682725f0","tid":2010143,"uid":42521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"私隱專員? 有呢個部門既咩?<br />\n警犬公開記者身分證, 影記者相放tg group果陣, 唔見影既又"},{"pid":"64d6283db9b440fe1a50ce4781236cb1acab43f8","tid":2010143,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"支持違法奪取主席位既係乜野職務呀？"},{"pid":"21be74d7e644a12256080bae408774943af24a18","tid":2010143,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61dd226542515aaa49b4fa162bb65dca145a57de","tid":2010143,"uid":3776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"起埋私穩專員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c036ffe6a870c85f0b9becb037bcaa6b682dab6a","tid":2010143,"uid":216888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"陶輝老婆